data.description: Come take a look at this 3 Bed, 2 Bath Home with a split floor plan, beautiful granite countertops in the kitchen, home office, and on a large corner lot, in the beautiful Copper Hill subdivision in Skiatook, Oklahoma! Close to schools, restaurants, and shopping, and just a 15 minute drive to Downtown Tulsa! The neighborhood also backs to walking trails and is near beautiful Skiatook Lake and the city park/splash pad!  Roof was replaced in 2020. Once under contract, seller will be having home professionally deep cleaned and all interior walls, ceilings, kitchen cabinets, bathroom cabinets, and trim throughout will be patched/painted by a professional painter, which has already been quoted, prior to closing! Buyer's may have a say in paint colors as well."
